All right, outside of indicting many cultures

07:13.800 --> 07:17.800
with their pizza attitudes, what is interesting and useful

07:17.800 --> 07:23.920
here is now this pizza component became far more useful to us.

07:23.920 --> 07:27.040
We get to create this encapsulated bit of logic

07:27.040 --> 07:29.920
that handles everything about having a pizza.

07:29.920 --> 07:33.920
So if you imagine working with our Padre Gino's website

07:33.920 --> 07:35.960
that we're about to go build, you

